&lt;p&gt;With At-Bay, our customers experience 5X fewer ransomware attacks. This is just the tip of the iceberg! &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.at-bay.com/press_releases/at-bay-launches-new-mdr-solution-for-smbs/&quot;&gt;Click here&lt;/a&gt; to learn more about what we&#39;re building.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
