&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Identification and analysis of anomalous activity in customer technology environments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Triage of event data to identity potential indicators of compromise&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134245417&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
